Subject: Re: [T2] Crane XR700 location

I've always mounted the XR700 module on the spare tire well.  My Ex 59, 61,
63, 67, 69, 71, & 73 Type 2s were all equipped with them clear back into the
early 70s (along with a 73 Toyota PU as well).  The module is sealed and no
damage from water is really possible.
